<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="halfway-adv">halfway <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌhɑːfˈweɪ/    美 /ˌhæfˈweɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>在中途；不彻底地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You will succeed in the end unless you give up halfway.
只要不半途而废，你终将成功。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was about <strong>halfway through</strong> his meal when a familiar voice came to his ears.
他饭吃到一半，忽然听到一个熟悉的声音。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Establish the right relationship at work and you're <strong>halfway there</strong>.
在工作中建立良好的人际关系，你就成功了一半。</p></div></div>